#: C/config-system.xml:857(title)
msgid "Modems"
msgstr "數據機"

#: C/config-system.xml:859(title)
msgid "Winmodems"
msgstr "Winmodems"

#: C/config-system.xml:860(para)
msgid ""
"Most winmodems are not supported by Kubuntu by default, but drivers can be "
"found that will enable the use of such modems. First you need to identify "
"what chipset your winmodem is using:"
msgstr ""
"大多數 winmodems 在 Kubuntu 下預設不能使用，但是能找到驅動程式來用這類數據機。首先您要確定您的 winmodem 使用的是什麼芯片："

#: C/config-system.xml:862(screen)
#, no-wrap
msgid ""
"\n"
"wget -c <ulink url=\"&scanmodem-url;\">&scanmodem-url;</ulink> \n"
"gunzip -c &scanmodem-gz; &gt; scanModem \n"
"chmod +x scanModem\n"
"sudo ./scanModem \n"
"kate Modem/ModemData.txt"
msgstr ""

#: C/config-system.xml:869(para)
msgid ""
"Check the output in Kate, it should list what modem chipset you have. Once "
"you are aware of the chipset you have, see <ulink "
"url=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/SettingUpModems\">SettingUpModems</ulink> and "
"follow the directions for your modem."
msgstr ""
"檢查 Kate 裡的內容，應該有列出您的數據機的芯片。一旦知道是什麼芯片，按照<ulink "
"url=\"https://wiki.ubuntu.com/Se"
"ttingUpModems\">SettingUpModems</ulink>設定你的數據機。"

#: C/config-system.xml:876(title)
msgid "ADSL Modems"
msgstr "ADSL 數據機"

#: C/config-system.xml:877(para)
